{"article_id":"ssYC1IDOi8UlIOZi","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Roger Stone Indictment Raises More Big Questions About Russia , Trump 2016 Campaign","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Justice Department added another piece to the puzzle of its Russia investigation on Friday with charges against GOP political consultant Roger Stone","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"- but the full picture still is n't complete .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Stone was arrested in Florida","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"following an indictment by a grand jury","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"working with the office of special counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Stone denied breaking the law","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"he 'll plead not guilty","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"when he 's arraigned later in Washington , D.C .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Prosecutors say","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Stone and at least two of his associates served as intermediaries between Donald Trump 's 2016 presidential campaign and `` Organization 1 ''","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"- as WikiLeaks is referred to in the court document -","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"which fenced material","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"stolen by the Russian government as part of the Kremlin 's scheme","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to wreak havoc in the 2016 White House race .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"After WikiLeaks released emails","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"stolen from the Democratic National Committee in July 2016 ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"`` a senior Trump campaign official was directed to contact Stone ''","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"to ask what else WikiLeaks had planned .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Stone then pinged `` Person 1 ''","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"- conservative commentator Jerome Corsi -","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"and instructed him to `` get the pending ... emails '' from WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"That was the start of what appeared to be weeks of indirect communication between the Trump campaign and WikiLeaks through Stone and his associates ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"according to the indictment","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"- and , via WikiLeaks , with Russia 's military intelligence agency , the GRU .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The charges","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Stone is facing","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"are about the accounts","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"he gave to Congress about these events .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Stone vowed Friday","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that he 'll fight the charges","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"he expects to be `` vindicated '' in court .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"A Trump lawyer highlighted on Friday","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"that the charges in the Stone indictment , however , are n't about collusion","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"- they 're about the statements","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Stone made to Congress and others .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"`` The indictment today does not allege Russian collusion by Roger Stone or anyone else , ''","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"said Trump personal attorney Jay Sekulow .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"`` Rather , the indictment focuses on alleged false statements","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Mr. Stone made to Congress . ''","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Sanders attempted to distance the president from the indictment and arrest .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"`` The president did nothing wrong , ''","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Sanders said in a Friday morning cable TV interview .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"`` There was no collusion . ''","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"And the president himself has frequently asserted via Twitter in the past two years","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that there was `` NO COLLUSION ! '' between his 2016 campaign and any Russian election interference effort","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"and called suggestions to the otherwise a `` hoax . ''","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Trump has also frequently referred to the Mueller investigation as a `` witch hunt . ''","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"The Stone indictment raises as many questions","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"as it answers .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Although the account","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"it gives","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"clarifies a few key points about the events of 2016 ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"there are also important things","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that it does n't say .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Did any of the Americans know","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"they were ultimately dealing with Russia ?","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"In the summer of 2016 , the fact of Russia 's `` active measures '' was the subject of speculation , anonymous quotes and supposition","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"- but was not officially confirmed in public .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Since then , Mueller 's office has detailed some of Russia 's practices :","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"the use of social media agitation","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"to deepen divisions among Americans","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"and the cyberattacks against political and other targets","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"in search of embarrassing dirt","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"to release .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"The question now is what Stone , Trump 's then-campaign chairman Paul Manafort , Trump 's family or Trump himself knew about what was taking place behind the scenes .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Trump has gone back and forth both then and now about what he accepts about the Russian election interference in 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"But at the time , he was consistent about how much he loved WikiLeaks","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and urged voters to focus on what it was revealing about the Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"no matter where the material was coming from .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"The events of July 2016 followed many contacts by Russians or their agents with people in the Trump campaign","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"- including a meeting the previous month","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"hosted by Donald Trump Jr. ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"following an offer of help for the campaign , again via intermediaries , from the Russian government .","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Manafort also met at least once with a business associate","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"who has been linked to the GRU","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"and ,","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"according to court documents ,","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"allegedly discussed polling data from the campaign ,","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"although the details about that meeting are n't clear .","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"even as Trump 's political fortunes improved throughout 2016 ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"he and his deputies were negotiating with powerful Russians behind the scenes over a potential Trump Tower project in Moscow .","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"But prosecutors have n't established","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"whether any contacts included information about Russia 's broader program of interference","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"or specifically whether anyone in Trump 's camp knew","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"that Russia was apparently behind the WikiLeaks releases .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Did Trump 's campaign know","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"what the Russians were doing ?","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Or did it embrace the support","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"it was getting","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"without being aware of its ultimate benefactor ?","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"WikiLeaks has denied","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"it received the stolen material from a Russian source .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"And it said on Friday of the Stone indictment","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that there was `` new evidence of no 'back channel ' with '' it .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"But ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"according to Mueller 's earlier indictment of 12 GRU officers ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"the Russian spies used the fake persona","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"they created ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"`` Guccifer 2.0 , ''","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"to give stolen material to WikiLeaks .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"Prosecutors have n't made clear","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"whether they believe","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Assange knew for certain","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"that he was actually dealing with the Russian government ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"although Secretary of State Mike Pompeo ,","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"when he was director of the CIA ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"declared unequivocally","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"that WikiLeaks is a `` hostile intelligence service . ''","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"In addition to the clandestine contacts , some actions took place in the open .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"Trump , for example , made a leitmotif of the emails","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"that Hillary Clinton deleted from the private server","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"she used","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"while she was secretary of state .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"On July 27 , 2016 , Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"`` Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"if you 're listening ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"I hope","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"you 're able to find the 30,000 emails","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"that are missing ...","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"you will probably be rewarded mightily by our press . ''","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"There are suggestions","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"that Russia was listening :","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"According to Mueller 's indictment of 12 GRU officers ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"the Russian spy agency ramped up its cyberattacks against Clinton and her presidential campaign that same day .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"Was Trump being facetious","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"because he considered all the discussion about Russian election interference to be a joke ?","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Or did he have reason","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"to expect","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"that someone in Russia might be paying attention","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"when he spoke ?","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"What communications did WikiLeaks potentially have with others in Stone 's circle ?","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"Much of the contact","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"that prosecutors contend","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"took place between Americans and WikiLeaks","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"allegedly","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"was actually via two Stone associates :","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"conservative commentator Jerome Corsi and radio host Randy Credico ,","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"who has denied being a link between WikiLeaks and Stone .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"A statement","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"issued by Corsi 's lawyers on Friday","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"says","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"the Stone indictment vindicates Corsi","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"- in Corsi 's view .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Although Corsi contends","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"that he testified truthfully before the grand jury and during his interviews with prosecutors ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"he may yet face charges of his own from the special counsel ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"as he has said","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"he has already walked away from a plea agreement about alleged lying about his actions .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"A passage in the indictment","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"unsealed on Friday","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"suggested","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"that someone was telling Corsi not only about WikiLeaks ' intentions , but also about messaging for use against Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"Specifically , Corsi began to recommend to Stone","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"that Clinton needed to be portrayed as unhealthy .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"`` Would not hurt to start suggesting HRC old , memory bad ,","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"has stroke","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"- neither he nor she well , ''","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"he wrote on Aug. 2 ,","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"according to the indictment .","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"`` I expect that much of next dump focus ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"setting stage for Foundation debacle . ''","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"In fact , neither Clinton 's health nor the Clinton Foundation were the focus of the next WikiLeaks release ,","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"but a messaging campaign","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"based on Clinton 's supposed ill health","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"took off in August 2016 .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"Russia 's state-controlled RT news site mentioned Clinton 's `` bad health , ''","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"the National Enquirer published a piece about it ,","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"Fox News host Sean Hannity discussed it on TV ,","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"and then Trump himself was warning about Clinton 's fitness by Aug. 18 .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"What action did the Trump campaign take","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"based on its alleged communications with WikiLeaks ?","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"Stone took credit ,","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"according to the indictment","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"unsealed Friday ,","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"for telling the Trump campaign beforehand about the Oct. 7 , 2016 , release by WikiLeaks of emails","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"stolen from Clinton 's campaign chairman , John Podesta .","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"He has said since","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"that he did n't have any inside information","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"and he was just puffing up his own importance","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"- taking things","depth":15},{"id":185,"text":"Assange was saying publicly","depth":15},{"id":186,"text":"and making it appear to Trump 's campaign","depth":15},{"id":187,"text":"that Stone had learned them through some kind of inside line .","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"Trump 's lawyer , Rudy Giuliani , said in December","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"that Stone had n't given the campaign a heads-up","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"but that","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"even if he had","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"- as prosecutors now allege -","depth":15},{"id":193,"text":"that is n't a crime .","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"Giuliani compared it to getting a tip","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"that a newspaper is about to run a story","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"before it appears .","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"And Stone ,","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"as he and others observed on Friday ,","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"is n't facing criminal charges","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"related to the actions","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"he took in 2016 ,","depth":13},{"id":202,"text":"but rather the accounts","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"he has given about them afterward to Congress and other related activity .","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"If that suggests","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"prosecutors do n't consider Stone 's underlying conduct itself to be illegal ,","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"it also raises questions about what he or Trump campaign leaders expected out of the warning about the Oct. 7 disclosure .","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"What actions did they take","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"- or not take -","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"with that information , if any ?","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":419,"left":0,"right":418,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":418,"left":258,"right":417,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":242,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":234,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":218,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":211,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":213,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":3,"right":212,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":6,"right":215,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":215,"left":7,"right":214,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":214,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":223,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":10,"right":222,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":222,"left":219,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":13,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":229,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":226,"right":228,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":226,"left":224,"right":225,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":224,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":227,"right":22,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":227,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa